_01_03_med.jpg\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/amnesty-rohingya/report_media/03_military/03_01_03_high.jpg 1920w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/amnesty-rohingya/report_media/03_military/03_01_03_lg.jpg 960w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/amnesty-rohingya/report_media/03_military/03_01_03_med.jpg 640w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/amnesty-rohingya/report_media/03_military/03_01_03_small.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"report_photo\" alt=\"\" /\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\u003cfont color=\"gray\"\u003e Source: Facebook posts, saved and on file with Amnesty International\u003c/font\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eSoldiers from the 33rd LID after arriving to northern Rakhine State.\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e","unique_id":"03_military_01"},{"animation":true,"animation_layers":[{"id":"03_military_buildings","method":"fade_in","type":"fill"},{"id":"03_military_school","method":"fade_in","type":"fill"}],"detail":{"chapter":"Military in Chut Pyin","end_date":"","long_description":"Residents from both the Rohingya and ethnic Rakhine parts of Chut Pyin told Amnesty International that soldiers from the 33rd LID slept in the school and Buddhist monastery located in the ethnic Rakhine part of the village. Those soldiers would play the leading role in the brutal attack on the Rohingya in and around Chut Pyin in the weeks that followed.","moment_date":"","short_description":"","start_date":"","title":"Soldiers Stay in Schoolhouse"},"interactive_layers":[],"layers":["02_03_BGPCamp_point","02_BGPCamp_label","02_zaydipyin_hamlet","02_zaydipyin_hamlet_label","03_military_buildings","03_military_school","03_villageCluster_brackets","03_villageCluster_labels","02_other_labels","04_base_label","04_school_label"],"map":{"before_after":false,"before_style":"","interactive":false,"load_new_basemap":false,"settings":{"center":"92.64075,20.569","controls":false,"mapbox_style":"mapbox://styles/situmapping/cjgntf2f0000h2tpsicjqmfgr","max_bounds":[[92.6,20.5383],[92.71,20.6]],"max_zo